'''Mandalore's armor''' was a traditional [[Mandalorian battle armor]] worn by [[Canderous Ordo]]<ref name="TSL">''[[Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic II: The Sith Lords]]''</ref> after the [[Jedi Civil War]],<ref name="KotOR">''[[Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic]]''</ref> as he assumed the position of [[Mandalore (title)/Legends|''Mand'alor'']] as Mandalore the Preserver.<ref name="KotORCG">''[[Knights of the Old Republic Campaign Guide]]''</ref> By the time of the [[First Jedi Purge]], during the travels of Canderous Ordo with [[Meetra Surik]] , the [[Armor/Legends|armor]] was still in exceptional condition despite the numerous battles it had seen. It was said that Mandalore never voluntarily took it off, even while sleeping.<ref name="TSL" />

